org.apache.accumulo.core.client.mapred

Class AbstractInputFormat.AbstractRecordReader<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.accumulo.core.client.mapred.AbstractInputFormat.AbstractRecordReader<K,V>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    InputFormatBase.RecordReaderBase
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractInputFormat<K,V>

    protected abstract static class AbstractInputFormat.AbstractRecordReader<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract base class to be used to create org.apache.hadoop.mapred.RecordReader instances that convert from Accumulo Key/Value pairs to the user's K/V types. Subclasses must implement #next(Object, Object) to update key and value, and also to update the following variables:
    • Key currentKey (used for progress reporting)
    • int numKeysRead (used for progress reporting)
